				<h3 class="bottomSpace">Anthony Nystrom, CTO &amp; Chief Architect</h3>
				
				<p>
					Anthony Nystrom is an accomplished software architect, engineer and versatilist 
					with 12 years proven experience building desktop, enterprise and internet applications. 
					His comprehensive expertise in technical design and development enable Next2Friends to 
					incorporate a multitude of technologies, platforms and programming languages into its 
					platform and roadmap.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Anthony has a BSc in Computer Science &amp; Mathematics, a BA in Biology &amp; Anthropology 
					and currently has 3 US software patents pending.
				</p>
				
				<h3 class="bottomSpace">Andrew Doyle, COO</h3>
				
				<p>
					Andrew Doyle is a global business executive focused on driving long-lasting financial 
					and operational success for both established global corporations and start-ups for 
					the last 20 years. Andrew’s work in the IT and telecoms industry has generated a 
					wealth of senior industry relationships, and he has worked for companies including 
					Fujitsu, Energis, Racal Telecom and Global Crossing. 
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Andrew has a degree in Business Studies, an Advanced Diploma in Marketing and 
